        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName>Down Farnborough Kent</placeName>
                    <date>July 30<hi rend="superscript">th</hi></date>
                    <salute>My dear Lord</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>I am much obliged for your Lordships very kind invitation to Chevening for the 3<hi rend="superscript">d</hi> of August, but I am sorry to say that I have friends in my house &amp; cannot do myself the honour of accepting your kindness.— I beg to remain | Your Lordships | Faithfully &amp; obliged | Charles Darwin</p> 
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
        
    
        
